ages/base/champions/little/Blitzcrank.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>BLITZCRANK</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">6</span> -&gt; 8,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Janna.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>JANNA</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">9</span> -&gt; 11,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Karma.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>KARMA</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">6</span> -&gt; 8,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Lulu.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>LULU</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">8,5</span> -&gt; 11\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Morgana.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>MORGANA</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">6</span> -&gt; 8,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Nami.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>NAMI</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">9</span> -&gt; 11,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Sona.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>SONA</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">9</span> -&gt; 11,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Soraka.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>SORAKA</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">9</span> -&gt; 11,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/TahmKench.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>TAHM KENCH</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: 5,5 -&gt; 8\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Taric.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>TARIC</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">6</span> -&gt; 8,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Zilean.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>ZILEAN</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">6</span> -&gt; 8,5\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft" src="http://www.onlol.net/style/images/base/champions/little/Zyra.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /><strong>ZYRA</strong>\r\n\r\nRegeneración de maná básica: <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">6</span> -&gt; 8,5', 'PARCHE 5.22', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '594-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-07 18:39:57', '2016-01-07 18:39:57', '', 594, 'http://news.onlol.net/index.php/2016/01/07/594-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
