(643, 2, '2016-01-08 13:27:40', '2016-01-08 13:27:40', '<strong>RECORDATORIO</strong>: El <strong>PBE</strong> es un campo de prueba para los cambios en League of Legends. Lo que pueda verse aquí puede no verse en las notas de los parches. Recordar que los desarrolladores de Legue of legends quieren vuestras opiniones, por lo que si no estáis de acuerdo con cualquiera de los cambios, podéis dejar vuestras opiniones en el <a href="http://boards.pbe.leagueoflegends.com/es/">PBE Community Forums</a>.\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>CAMBIOS A CAMPEONES</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Fiddlesticks-Final-Portrait-1.jpg" alt="Fiddlesticks-Final-Portrait (1)" /></p>\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-53263 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Dark-Wind-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Dark Wind Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Viento siniestro - E</strong>\r\n\r\nLos costes de maná decaen de <del><em>50/70/90/110/130</em></del> a 50/60/70/80/90.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Gangplank-Final-Champion-Portrait-1.jpg" alt="Gangplank-Final-Champion-Portrait (1)" />\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-53175 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Trial-by-Fire-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Trial by Fire Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Prueba de fuego - PASIVA</strong>\r\n\r\nBonus Ad ratio disminuyen de <em><del>1.2</del></em> a 1.\r\nDuración del DoT (daño por segundo) aumenta de <del><em>1.5</em></del> a 2.5 segundos (mismo daño).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kalista-Final-Portrait.jpg" alt="Kalista Final Portrait" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Desgarrar - E </strong><strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52753 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Rend-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Rend Final Icon" width="64" height="64" /></strong>\r\n\r\nEl coste de maná disminuye de <del><em>40</em></del> en todos los rangos a 30.\r\n\r\nNo habrá reset de mána cuando Desgarrar mate su objetivo. Las muertes posteriores reseteará el coste total (30).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Khazix-Final-Portrait.jpg" alt="Khazix Final Portrait" />\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-54088 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Leap-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Leap Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Salto - E </strong>\r\n\r\nEl rango desciende de <em><del>600</del></em> a 700.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/LeBlanc-Final-Portrait.jpg" alt="LeBlanc Final Portrait" />\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52686 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Ethereal-Chains-Final-Icon-1.jpg" alt="Ethereal Chains Final Icon (1)" width="64" height="64" />Cadenas etéreas - E </strong>\r\n\r\nAumenta la velocidad del misíl de <del><em>1600</em></del> a 1750.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Miss-Fortune-Final-Portrait.jpg" alt="Miss Fortune Final Portrait" />\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-483 size-full alignleft" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Make-it-Rain-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Make-it-Rain-Final-Icon" width="64" height="64" /> <strong>Lluvia de plomo - E</strong>\r\nDaño de base disminuye de <em><del>90/145/200/225/310</del></em> a 80/115/150/220.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Mordekaiser-Final-Portrait.jpg" alt="Mordekaiser Final Portrait" />\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52751 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Iron-Man-Final-Icon-1.jpg" alt="Iron Man Final Icon (1)" width="64" height="64" />Hombre de hierro - PASIVA</strong>\r\n\r\nEl escudo decae de un <em><del>2%</del></em> por segundo a 1.5%\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52989 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Harvester-of-Sorrow-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Harvester of Sorrow Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Cosechadores de pesar - W</strong>\r\n\r\nEl hechizo se puede lanzar ahora sobre los súbditos y permite a Mordekaiser lanzar el toque de daño en aura.\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52831 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Children-of-the-Grave-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Children of the Grave Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Hijos de la tumba - R</strong>\r\n\r\nAhora el 25% de su daño instantaneo disminuye al 50% (daño total sin cambios, DOT del 75% al 50%).\r\n\r\nBonus AD en Ghost se ha cambiado de 10.25.50 a (1.0 del Bonus AD de Mordekaiser).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Teemo-Final-Champion-Portrait.jpg" alt="Teemo Final Champion Portrait" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/GENERAL-Banner1.jpg" alt="GENERAL Banner" />\r\n\r\nDaño de ataque básico aumenta de <del><em>47.5</em></del> a 49.5.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft wp-image-53271 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Camouflage-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Camouflage Final Icon" width="64" height="64" /><strong>Camuflaje - PASSIVA</strong>\r\n\r\nEl tiempo de sigilo en el seto aumenta de <del><em>0,75</em></del> segundos a 1,5.\r\n\r\nTeemo puede estar ahora en sigilo mientras se mueve por el seto.\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-53274 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Noxious-Trap-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Noxious Trap Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Trampa perjudicial - R </strong>\r\n\r\nEl rango aumenta de <em><del>300/600/900</del></em> a 400/650/900.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Trundle-Final-Portrait-1.jpg" alt="Trundle-Final-Portrait (1)" />\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52640 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Pillar-of-Ice-Final-Icon-1-1.jpg" alt="Pillar-of-Ice-Final-Icon (1) (1)" width="64" height="64" />Pilar de hielo - E </strong>\r\n\r\nEl coste de maná aumenta de <em><del>60</del></em> en todos los rangos a 75.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>AJUSTES A OBJETOS</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-53761 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Deaths-Dance-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Deaths Dance Final Icon" width="64" height="64" hspace="0" vspace="20" />Baile de la muerte</strong>\r\n\r\nLa curación de su pasiva única aumenta de un <em><del>12%</del></em> del daño infligido a 15%;\r\n\r\nEl daño de efecto de sangrado (DoT) aumenta de <em><del>12%</del></em> a 15%.\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">El daño de ataque aumenta de <em><del>65</del></em> a 75.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">El coste de la receta aumenta de 525 de oro a 625 (el coste total aumenta de 3400 de oro a 3500).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52846 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Eye-of-the-Oasis-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Eye of the Oasis Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Ojo del Oasis</strong>\r\n\r\nAhora concede un 10% de Reducción de enfriamiento.\r\n\r\nEl Bonus de regeneración de maná disminuye de un <em><del>150%</del></em> a 100%.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-52845 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Eye-of-the-Watchers-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Eye of the Watchers Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Ojo de los vigilantes\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nAhora concede un 10% de Reducción de enfriamiento.\r\n\r\nBonus de regeneración de maná disminuye de un <em><del>150%</del></em> a 100%.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><img class="alignleft wp-image-53195 size-full" src="http://www.newsoflegends.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Farsight-Alteration-Final-Icon.jpg" alt="Farsight Alteration Final Icon" width="64" height="64" />Visión de lejanía modificada</strong>\r\n\r\nDisminuye el enfriamiento del Talismán un 33%, aumentando un 50% [los valores son casi idénticos por el brillo del Talismán].\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>AJUSTES A MORGANA ESPECTRO LUNAR</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Se ha iluminado y se le han añadido más detalles a la forma de Morgana espectro lunar. Las dos primeras fotos son del modelo antiguo y las dos últimas el nuevo.\r\nMorgana espectro lunar es una <strong>Skin Legendaria</strong> que costará <strong>975 RP''s</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-484 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Wraith-Morgana-Model-1-1024x640.jpg" alt="Wraith-Morgana-Model-1" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-485 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Wraith-Morgana-model-2-1024x640.jpg" alt="Wraith-Morgana-model-2" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-486 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/vvvv-1024x640.jpg" alt="vvvv" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-487 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/vvvvvvvvvvvvv-1024x640.jpg" alt="vvvvvvvvvvvvv" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>AJUSTES A WUKONG RADIANTE</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Wukong radiante ha sido modificado para ser... más radiante aún. Las dos primeras fotos son del modelo antiguo y las dos últimas del nuevo.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-490 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Radiant-Wukong-Model-1-1024x640.jpg" alt="Radiant-Wukong-Model-1" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-491 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Radiant-Wukong-Model-2-1024x640.jpg" alt="Radiant-Wukong-Model-2" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-492 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/mmm-1024x640.jpg" alt="mmm" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-493 size-large" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/bbbb-1024x640.jpg" alt="bbbb" width="1024" height="640" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>NUEVOS ICONOS DE EQUIPOS</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Los nuevos iconos de equipo para la sexta temporada ya están disponibles en el PBE. Su precio es de <strong>250 RP''s</strong> y como siempre, parte de los beneficios irán destinos a los respectivos equipos:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Oceanía</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-494" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/oc1.jpg" alt="oc1" width="90" height="90" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-495" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/oc2.jpg" alt="oc2" width="90" height="90" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-496" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/oc3.jpg" alt="oc3" width="90" height="90" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-497" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/oc4.jpg" alt="oc4" width="90" height="90" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-498" src="http://news.onlol.net/wp